2000-08-01  Geoffrey T. Dairiki  <dairiki@dairiki.org>

	* wiki_config.php3, admin.php3: Cleanup determination
	of $ScriptName, et. al.

	* wiki_ziplib.php3: Never use gzcompress().  It outputs its
	compressed data with different headers/checksum than the gzip
	format obtained through the used of gzopen()/gzwrite().

2000-07-31  Geoffrey T. Dairiki  <dairiki@dairiki.org>

	* index.php3: Added total page generation time to {DebugInfo}.
	(PHP4 is really quite a speed improvement over PHP3!)

	* wiki_diff.php3: PHP4 fixes. If $t is an array, under PHP3
	'$t > 0' is false while under PHP4 it is true.  Also '0 + $t'
	generates a run-time error ("unsupported operand types") under
	PHP4, but not under PHP3.
	
	* wiki_renderlib.php3: Move initialization of a number of class
	variables into class constructors.  (This is for PHP4, which
	doesn't seem to like anything but simple literals as initializers
	for var declarations within a class.)

	* wiki_diff.php3, wiki_display.php3:  Use getPage() instead of
	retrievePage() to avoid errors for non-existing pages.
	* wiki_stdlib.php3 (UpdateRecentChanges):  Ditto.

	* wiki_template.php3: Bug fixes for some bad token reference
	warning messages.
	
	* wiki_template.php3: Change "{$what}" to "\{$what}" in an effort
	to make code PHP4 compatible.

	* templates/error.html: Bug fix.
	* templates/save.html: Minor cleanup.

2000-07-30  Geoffrey T. Dairiki  <dairiki@dairiki.org>

	* wiki_config.php3: set_magic_quotes_runtime(0).

	* wiki_dbmlib.php3: Sort pages returned by retrieveAllPages().

	* DBLIB.txt: Beginnings of documentation of the API to my hacked
	database interface.

